It is newly discovered steroid which have very strong anabolic and androgenic effects. It creates a very pronounced anabolic effect which start to manifests itself within days and increase in mass, strength and glycogen synthesis. This creates a significant weight gain in first weeks of use. Since this steroid is a new scientific discovery and extremely powerful molecule, all users should threat it with respect and do not exceed recommended dosage

SUPERBULK-2

2-Oxamethyl Dienolone is an injectable derivative of the anabolic steroid nandrolone. It is 36 times more powerful than Nandrolone and 8-9 times more powerful than Trenbolone. It is newly discovered steroid which have very strong anabolic and androgenic effects. It creates a very pronounced anabolic effect which start to manifests itself within days and increase in mass, strength and glycogen synthesis. This creates a significant weight gain in first weeks of use. Since this steroid is a new scientific discovery and extremely powerful molecule, all users should threat it with respect and do not exceed recommended dosage

DOSAGE
The usual dosage for physique- or performance-enhancing purposes is the range of minimum 1 to maximum 2 ml per day, taken in cycles 6-8 weeks in length.This level is sufficient for most users to notice high level gains in lean muscle mass and strength. Before starting this cycle of 6-8 weeks, user must first use
